</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=State+Bar+of+Michigan&amp;rft.atitle=Unauthorized+Practice+of+Law&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michbar.org%2Ffile%2Fprofessional%2Fpdfs%2Fuplfacts.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Kao, Frances P. (2 January 2007). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://apps.americanbar.org/buslaw/blt/2007-01-02/kao.shtml\">\"No, a paralegal is not a lawyer\"</a>. <i>Business Law Today</i>. <b>16</b> (3)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Business+Law+Today&amp;rft.atitle=No%2C+a+paralegal+is+not+a+lawyer&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.date=2007-01-02&amp;rft.aulast=Kao&amp;rft.aufirst=Frances+P.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.americanbar.org%2Fbuslaw%2Fblt%2F2007-01-02%2Fkao.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.isba.org/sites/default/files/committees/upl/uplfaq.pdf\">\"IS BA and the Unauthorized Practice of Law - What The Public Needs To Know\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Illinois State Bar Association</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Illinois+State+Bar+Association&amp;rft.atitle=IS+BA+and+the+Unauthorized+Practice+of+Law+-+What+The+Public+Needs+To+Know&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.isba.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcommittees%2Fupl%2Fuplfaq.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.oecd.org/regreform/sectors/40080343.pdf\">\"Competitive Restrictions in Legal Professions\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>OECD</i>. Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development. 27 April 2009<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=OECD&amp;rft.atitle=Competitive+Restrictions+in+Legal+Professions&amp;rft.date=2009-04-27&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd.org%2Fregreform%2Fsectors%2F40080343.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Roy, Alex; Handford, Chris. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.legalservicesboard.org.uk/Projects/rationalising_scope_of_regulation/pdf/reserved_and_unreserved_lawyers.pdf\">\"Reserved and Unreserved Lawyers' Activities\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Legal Services Board</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Legal+Services+Board&amp;rft.atitle=Reserved+and+Unreserved+Lawyers%E2%80%99+Activities&amp;rft.aulast=Roy&amp;rft.aufirst=Alex&amp;rft.au=Handford%2C+Chris&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legalservicesboard.org.uk%2FProjects%2Frationalising_scope_of_regulation%2Fpdf%2Freserved_and_unreserved_lawyers.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Plant, Charles (18 August 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.lawgazette.co.uk/analysis/the-definition-of-reserved-legal-activities-should-be-extended/61811.article\">\"The definition of reserved legal activities should be extended\"</a>. The Law Society Gazette<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+definition+of+reserved+legal+activities+should+be+extended&amp;rft.date=2011-08-18&amp;rft.aulast=Plant&amp;rft.aufirst=Charles&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawgazette.co.uk%2Fanalysis%2Fthe-definition-of-reserved-legal-activities-should-be-extended%2F61811.article&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Fischer, Julee C. (2000). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mckinneylaw.iu.edu/ILR/pdf/vol34p121.pdf\">\"Policing the Self-Help Legal Market: Consumer Protection or Protection of the Legal Cartel\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Indiana Law Review</i>. <b>34</b>: 121<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Indiana+Law+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Policing+the+Self-Help+Legal+Market%3A+Consumer+Protection+or+Protection+of+the+Legal+Cartel&amp;rft.volume=34&amp;rft.pages=121&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.aulast=Fischer&amp;rft.aufirst=Julee+C.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fmckinneylaw.iu.edu%2FILR%2Fpdf%2Fvol34p121.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hirealawyer.findlaw.com/do-you-need-a-lawyer/what-is-legal-advice.html\">\"What is 'Legal Advice'?\"</a>. FindLaw<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">23 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=What+is+%27Legal+Advice%27%3F&amp;rft.pub=FindLaw&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fhirealawyer.findlaw.com%2Fdo-you-need-a-lawyer%2Fwhat-is-legal-advice.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALegal+advice\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Denckla, Derek A. (1999). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"ht